### 1. Attribution Requirement / The “Remember The Name” Clause

The above copyright notice and this permission notice shall be included in all copies or substantial portions of the Software—because this is **50% power, 50% pain**, and the receipt stays on the chain. Keep the credit where it lives: in the header, in the file, in the fork, in the sale. Remix the code, rewrite the flow, ship it anywhere you wanna go—**but don’t strip the tag**, don’t blank the name, don’t pretend it fell from the sky without someone paying the cost to make it.

